  "title": "Class 3 Delivery Driver / Food Wholesale Company @ Admiralty / 5.5 Work Week",
  "description": "<p>As the Delivery Driver, you are expected to perform the following key responsibilities:<br>\n<br>\n• Deliver food items to various locations.<br>\n• Collect items from cargo or suppliers.<br>\n• Ensure secure loading and unloading of food items into the vehicle.<br>\n• Verify all items match delivery orders.<br>\n• Ensure all goods are delivered in good condition and according to customer specifications.<br>\n• Follow traffic laws and drive safely<br>\n• Collect cash payments upon delivery<br>\n• Keep track of payments and report any issues.<br>\n• Achieve productivity targets set by the company<br>\n• Ensure that deliveries are running smoothly and on time.<br>\n• Ensure good delivery quality standards.<br>\n• Address any customer issues professionally.<br>\n• Assist the warehouse team with packing duties when available.<br>\n• Assist with checking inventory and managing stock.<br>\n• Keep vehicle clean and in good shape.<br>\n• Arrange for regular maintenance and repairs.<br>\n• Follow safety and health rules to ensure personal compliance.<br>\n• Report any safety or health incidents<br>\n• Perform other ad-hoc duties / project as assigned by Superior.</p>\n<h3><strong>Requirement</strong></h3>\n<p>• Possess valid Singapore Class 3 licence.<br>\n• Capable of driving 10-foot lorry.<br>\n• Able to work in enviornment with extreme cold temperatures or under the hot sun.<br>\n• Capable of lifting heavy items weighing above 20kg<br>\n• Responsible and meticulous in managing warehouse stock.<br>\n• A team player with strong communmication and interpersonal skills.<br>\n• Possess strong time management and problem solving skills.</p>",
